{"tid":2362527,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"張舉能: 未來有不少於7宗有關社會事件案件 會於上訴庭處理刑期覆核","createTime":"2021-01-11T13:22:55.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-11T14:30:30.000Z","uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"6b34e3373bf5ce12642d72c8e2c0bd027e8f7818","tid":2362527,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T13:22:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_info/4937\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_info%2F4937&d=bDhD0m8o4fsrNJ%2BdslRS%2BQi%2F3qgDO6vJfpFVPRJtUZY%3D&h=5c33f4c8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_info/4937</a><br />\n<br />\n【頭條日報】今日宣誓就職的終審法院首席法官張舉能在會見傳媒時表示，上訴和審刑覆核已屬最有效及常規的方法，消除各下級法院之間判刑差異。<br />\n<br />\n他又指，上訴法庭至今已經一共處理了不少於8宗社會事件有關的案件的判刑覆核，並就這類案件發出重要量刑的指引和指導，相關指導對所有下級法院具有約束力，未來亦會有不少於7宗類似案件會處理。（全文 )<br />\n<br />\n附: 終審法院首席法官二○二一年法律年度開啟典禮演辭<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/202101/11/P2021011100557.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F202101%2F11%2FP2021011100557.htm&d=bDhD0m8o4fsrNJ%2BdslRS%2BQi%2F3qgDO6vJfpFVPRJtUZY%3D&h=e453d5a8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/202101/11/P2021011100557.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n#20210111新聞"},{"pid":"44f88b95fa49c0e2cde776ddccfab72b4d00a544","tid":2362527,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T13:25:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15f4d5192b56fbbf06abf3ea04cf51fa36e42997","tid":2362527,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"44f88b95fa49c0e2cde776ddccfab72b4d00a544","tid":2362527,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T13:25:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" cla